text:
Daniel - there can be a variety of things happening with this error. One recommended fix is to go to Settings -> System -> Processor and assign more than 2 processor cores.
It can also be caused if you haven't enabled Virtualization - so you might want to verify that is turned on.
If neither of those addresses the issue, there are a lot of other people who have had this problem before. Just make sure you focus your searches with the "virtualbox" keyword when you search for forums and websites discussing the error.

elements.text:
